com.cubeia.firebase.api.util
Interface UnmodifiableList<T>

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<T>
All Known Subinterfaces:
StringList
public interface UnmodifiableList<T>
extends Iterable<T>

A simple iterable interface for unmodifiable lists. The purpose of this interface is to provide a trivial wrapper for underlying data models. This list is zero-indexed.

Author:
Lars J. Nilsson
